snippet.title: Sentencing Phase Underway for Ex-Dallas Officer Amber Guyger | Part 2
snippet.description: The Sentencing Phase of Amber Guyger was underway at a Texas courthouse on Oct. 1, 2019. Guyger, a former Dallas police officer, could be facing decades in prison after being convicted of murder Tuesday in the fatal shooting of her black, unarmed neighbor who she said she believed was an intruder in her home. http://on.ktla.com/DWVZM #AmberGuyger #BothamJean
